Invocation Name: number knowledge
des:
Brush up on your number trivia!

Did you know that the number "98" is the highest jersey number allowed in the NHL?
Or that "123" is the emergency number in Columbia?
I bet you didn't know that "7,000,000" was the estimated world population on October, 2011!

Get access to all these facts by using Numbers!
